query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mi t mc) NoMergeJoin(mc mi t ak) NoMergeJoin(ak mc mi t mk) */ select min(mi.info) AS release_date,
min(t.title) AS modern_internet_movie
from movie_info AS mi
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.note like '%internet%' AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND ( mi.info like 'USA:% 199%' OR mi.info like 'USA:% 200%') AND t.production_year < 2006
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join aka_title AS ak
on t.id = ak.movie_id
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id;
